Responsibilities:

Communicating with oversea buyer to handle the whole design process from theme board preparation, styling confirmation, fitting sessions to pre-production stage;
Researching of seasonal themes, material and colors;
Product analysis on materials, consumption, sewing structure.
Work closely with merchandising and factories to facilitate development processes;
