 Requirements:

Degree holder in Fashion Design, Textiles & Clothing or related disciplines;
1-4 year experience of product development in sportswear/ active wear / casual wear.

Adaptable to system and strong in computer skill. 
Self-motivated, good interpersonal skills and detail-oriented;
Good command of English, Chinese & Mandarin;
Familiar with Photoshop, Illustrator, MS Office - Word, Excel, PowerPoint. 
Skillful in apparel 3D software - such as Browzwear, CLO, Optitex is preferable. 
Immediate available is preferred.

